/the-blade-mw0002852794 Allmusic, The Blade ]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2015\n| ''  Pocket Full of Keys    ''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Dale Ann Bradley\n| Vocals <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/pocket-full-of-keys-mw0002843846/releases Allmusic, Pocket Full of Keys ]</ref>\n|-\n\n \t \t\n| 2015\n| ''  Valley of the Snake    ''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Ruby the Hatchet \t\n| Lap Steel Guitar  <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/valley-of-the-snake-mw0002796588 Allmusic,Valley of the Snake ]</ref>\n|-\n \t\n| 2016\n| ''[[Full Circle (Loretta Lynn album)|Full Circle]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Loretta Lynn]]\n| Vocals, Guitar <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/full-circle-mw0002898188 Allmusic, Full Circle, Loretta Lynn]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2016\n| ''[[The Earls of Leicester (band)#Discography|Rattle & Roar]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[The Earls of Leicester (band)|The Earls of Leicester]]\n| Vocals, Mandolin, Group Member <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/rattle-amp-roar-mw0002950966 Allmusic, Rattle & Roar]</ref><ref>[http://www.countrystandardtime.com/news/newsitem.asp?xid=9092 countrystandardtime.com, Rattle & Roar Review]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2016\n| ''The Fiddler's Dream''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Michael Cleveland\n| Guitar, vocals, mixer, producer, Grammy Nomination<ref>[http://compassrecords.com/artist/michael-cleveland/ compassrecords.com, The Fiddler's Dream]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2018\n| ''King of the Road: A Tribute to Roger Mille''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  \tVarious Artists\n| Mandolin, Vocal <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/king-of-the-road-a-tribute-to-roger-miller-mw0003193154, Allmusic, King of the Road: A Tribute to Roger Mille]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2018\n| '' Tis Ol War''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  \t Coco O'Connor\n| Mandolin, Vocal <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/this-ol-war-mw0003168833/releases, Allmusic, Tis Ol War]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2018\n| ''Live at the CMA Theater in the Country Music Hall of