6085 Allmusic, Delayed but Not Denied]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2002\n| ''[[Down the Old Plank Road: The Nashville Sessions]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;| [[The Chieftains]]\n| Engineer, Vocals, Guitar, Vocals Producer, Grammy nominated <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/down-the-old-plank-road-the-nashville-sessions-mw0000223831 Allmusic, Down the Old Plank Road: The Nashville Sessions]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2002\n| '' O Sister 2: A Women's Bluegrass Collection''\n| style=\"text-align:center;| Various Artists\n| Guitar <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/o-sister-2-a-womens-bluegrass-collection-mw0000228537 Allmusic, O Sister 2: A Women's Bluegrass Collection]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2002\n| ''[[Jim Hurst#Discography|Second Son]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;| [[Jim Hurst]]\n| Vocals <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/second-son-mw0000659249 Allmusic,Second Son]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2002\n| '' The Angels Are Singing: A Women's Bluegrass Gospel Collection''\n| style=\"text-align:center;| Various Artists\n| Vocals <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/the-angels-are-singing-a-womens-bluegrass-gospel-collection-mw0000227211 Allmusic, The Angels Are Singing: A Women's Bluegrass Gospel Collection]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2002\n| ''The Singer-Songwriter Collection''\n| style=\"text-align:center;| Various Artists\n| Vocals <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/the-singer-songwriter-collection-mw0000219252 Allmusic, The Singer-Songwriter Collection]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2002 \t\n| ''Flame Keeper ''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Michael Cleveland]]\n| Producer, Mixer, Vocals <ref>[https://www.discogs.com/Michael-Cleveland-Flame-Keeper/release/4060021 discogs.com, Flame Keeper, Michael Cleveland]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2003\n| ''Blue Ridge Mountain Mandolin''\n| style=\"text-align:center;| Various Artists\n| Guitar <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/blue-ridge-mountain-mandolin-mw0000023992 Allmusic,  Blue Ridge Mountain Mandolin]</ref>\n|-\n \t\n\n| 2003 \t\n| '' Bluegrass Today ''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\