iew]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2016\n| ''The Fiddler's Dream''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Michael Cleveland\n| Guitar, vocals, mixer, producer, Grammy Nomination<ref>[http://compassrecords.com/artist/michael-cleveland/ compassrecords.com, The Fiddler's Dream]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2018\n| ''King of the Road: A Tribute to Roger Mille''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  \tVarious Artists\n| Mandolin, Vocal <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/king-of-the-road-a-tribute-to-roger-miller-mw0003193154, Allmusic, King of the Road: A Tribute to Roger Mille]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2018\n| '' Tis Ol War''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  \t Coco O'Connor\n| Mandolin, Vocal <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/this-ol-war-mw0003168833/releases, Allmusic, Tis Ol War]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2018\n| ''Live at the CMA Theater in the Country Music Hall of Fame''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| The Earls of Leicester\n| Vocals, Mandolin<ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/live-at-the-cma-theater-in-the-country-music-hall-of-fame-mw0003203494/releases Allmusic, Live at the CMA Theater in the Country Music Hall of Fame]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n| 2019\n| '' Love Hard, Work Hard, Play Hard ''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Deanie Richardson\n| Vocals <ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/love-hard-work-hard-play-hard-mw0003234325 Allmusic, Love Hard, Work Hard, Play Hard ]</ref>\n|\n|-\n\n|  2019\n| ''Tall Fiddler''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Michael Cleveland\n|  Producer  <ref>[https://bluegrasstoday.com/michael-cleveland-talks-tall-fiddler/ bluegrasstoday.com, Tall Fiddler, by Daniel Mullins August 23, 2019]</ref>\n|-\n|\n|\n|}\n\n===Performances===\n*Selected: Tours, Performances and Events.<ref>[https://airplaydirect.com/music/JeffWhiteTheBrokenRoad/ airplaydirect.com Jeff White]</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Event\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Artist\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Note\n|-\n|\n|-\n\n| 1987-1989\n| ''Alison Krauss tours''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Alison K