ieftains, February 1, 2013]</ref><ref>[https://irishamerica.com/2003/02/the-chieftains-will-tour-u-s/ irishamerica.com, The Chieftains Will Tour U.S. By Irish America Staff, February 2003]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2009\n| Mountain Soul II tour\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| Patty Loveless\n| Guitar, Vocals <ref>[https://bluegrasstoday.com/patty-loveless-mountain-soul-2/ bluegrasstoday.com, Patty Loveless \u2013 Mountain Soul II, by John Lawless, October 20, 2009]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2010 - 2017\n| ''The Travelin' McCourys tour''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| Travelin' McCourys\n|  Guitar, Vocals  <ref>[https://www.thetravelinmccourys.com/blog/big-news thetravelinmccourys.com  Travelin' McCourys  Big news!, November 12, 2015]</ref>\n|-\n\n| October 26, 2014\n| ''Country Music Hall of Fame Medallion Ceremony''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Various Artist\n|  Guitar, Vocals <ref>Country s Sweetest Night. Keeping It Nashville. October 27, 2014, Issue 420</ref><ref>[http://www.cybergrass.com/node/4151#sthash.am0CiH61.dpbs cybergrass.com, Country Music Hall of Fame Medallion Ceremony]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2000-2019 <br>(on and off since 2000)\n| Live at the Station Inn, Nashville\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| Jeff White\n|  Guitar, Vocals <ref>[https://www.nowplayingnashville.com/event/jeff-white-friends/ nowplayingnashville.com Jeff White Station Inn ]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2015\n|Flatpick Guitar Demonstration<br>[[Country Music Hall of Fame]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|  Jeff White\n|  Guitar <ref>[https://nashville.eventful.com/events/fiddle-and-flatpick-guitar-demonstration-laura-/E0-001-085741698-1 Jeff White Flatpick Guitar Demonstration, Country Music Hall of Fame, Nashville, August 16, 2015 ]</ref>\n|-\n\n| 2016-2019\n|The Earls Of Leicester Tours\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| The Earls Of Leicester\n|  Guitar, mandolin, Vocals <ref>[https://jerrydouglas.com/the-earls-of-leicester-live-at-the-cma-theater-in-the-country-music-hall-of-fame/ errydouglas.com, The Earls Of Leicester